      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-den-cab-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      30                   to   v-car                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      41                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-cod-cab-den (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
